    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you want to add 10 items to your <code>ArrayList</code> you may try that:</p>\n\n<pre><code>for (int i = 0; i &lt; 10; i++)\n    arr.add(i);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If you have already declare an array size variable you would use the variable <code>size</code> instead of number '10'</p>\n"
