    "body" : "<p>if you want to use Collections.fill(list, obj); in order to fill the list with a repeated object alternatively you can use</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt; arr=new ArrayList&lt;Integer&gt;(Collections.nCopies(10, 0));\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>the line copies 10 times 0 in to your ArrayList</p>\n"
