    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 7,
    "last_activity_date" : 1551157508,
    "creation_date" : 1551157508,
    "answer_id" : 54878740,
    "question_id" : 8896758,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Being late to this, but after <strong>Java 8</strong>, I personally find this following approach with the <code>Stream</code> API more concise and can be an alternative to <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/8896824/10734272\">the accepted answer</a>.</p>\n\n<p>For example,</p>\n\n<p><code>Arrays.stream(new int[size]).boxed().collect(Collectors.toList())</code></p>\n\n<p>where <code>size</code> is the desired <code>List</code> size and without <a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/8896758/initial-size-for-the-arraylist/36518805#comment39907288_23586315\">the disadvantage mentioned here</a>, all elements in the <code>List</code> are initialized as <code>0</code>.</p>\n\n<p>(I did a quick search and did not see <code>stream</code> in any answers posted - feel free to let me know if this answer is redundant and I can remove it)</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 4738305,
      "reputation" : 91,
      "user_id" : 3831989,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://graph.facebook.com/607393071/picture?type=large",
      "display_name" : "anch2150",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3831989/anch2150"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1567083185,
    "creation_date" : 1567083185,
    "answer_id" : 57710677,
    "question_id" : 8896758,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>My two cents on <code>Stream</code>. I think it's better to use</p>\n\n<pre><code>IntStream.generate(i -&gt; MyClass.contruct())\n         .limit(INT_SIZE)\n         .collect(Collectors.toList());\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>with the flexibility to put any initial values.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 20059025,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 14706143,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GhRvscWAaS9pAZ2oZbWKhggb2NktVunNKegIldT=k-s256",
